feat: Whelmed Phase 3 — Screen architecture, tokenization, config unification

Architecture:
- Blocks are data+render objects, not Components
- Screen: single paint() with viewport culling
- First-screen batch loading, incremental building via timer
- CodeBlock merged into TextBlock

Tokenization:
- Code syntax highlighting via JUCE CodeTokeniser
- GenericTokeniser for Python, JS, TS, Rust, Go, Bash, SQL, JSON, YAML, Swift

Config:
- WhelmedConfig moved to Source/config/
- DocConfig eliminated — Screen reads config directly
- StatusBarOverlay + LoaderOverlay unified at app level
- Oblivion TET palette applied throughout

Infrastructure:
- InputHandler decoupled from ScreenBase — routed through State
- Selection mode keyboard fix (buildKeyMap after construction)
- Mermaid onReady timing fix
- Hot reload wires both terminal and whelmed configs
- Display proportional font embedded (Book/Medium/Bold)
- DESIGN.md manifesto, PLAN-WHELMED.md rewritten
